    <h2 id="day-1-arriving-in-nantes">
      Day 1 - Arriving in Nantes
    </h2>

  <ul>
    <li><b>Route: Nantes to Saint-Nazaire</b></li><li><b>Distance:&nbsp;99km</b></li><li><b>Overnight spot: <a href="https://park4night.com/en/place/293293" target="_blank">Parking at&nbsp;Plage de la Courance</a></b></li>
  </ul>
<div><!-- Map container and overlay -->
